original: Lindström, Axel Erik Bertil, kyrkoherde, Dalhem, f. 14/4/07 i Gladhammar, Kalmar 1., av Axel L. o. Anna Pettersson. G. 37 m. Sonja Jonasson. Barn: Elisabeth f. 43. — Stud:ex. i Västervik 26, teol. fil. ex. 29, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov o. prästv. f. Linköp. stift 33. Varit past:adj. i Hannäs, Gamleby, Kristdala o. Vadstena, v. komm. i Misterhult, v. pastor i Överum samt kyrkoadj. i Mell-by, kyrkoh. i Dalhem sed. 39.
translated: Lindström, Axel Erik Bertil, vicar, Dalhem, b. 14/4/07 in Gladhammar, Kalmar 1st district, son of Axel L. and Anna Pettersson. Married in 1937 to Sonja Jonasson. Children: Elisabeth b. 1943. - Completed studentexamen in Västervik in 1926, theological bachelor's degree in 1929, theological licentiate, practical theological examination, and ordained as a priest in the Linköping diocese in 1933. Previously served as an assistant pastor in Hannäs, Gamleby, Kristdala, and Vadstena, temporary curate in Misterhult, assistant pastor in Överum, and curate in Mellby. Appointed vicar in Dalhem since 1939.
